5|$|Several victims <b>of</b> <b>the</b> <b>massacre</b> are honoured {{individually}} in Vukovar. There is {{a monument}} honouring Kačić {{together with his}} father who was killed on 2 October 1991 during the Battle of Vukovar, a bridge in the city is named after Nicolier, {{and one of the}} city's schools is named after Glavašević.|$|E
